# L1-5: Single PEC wedge — UTD diffraction validation
# 90-degree wedge: 0-face at x=2,y<0, n-face at x>2,y=0
# Edge from (2,0,-50) to (2,0,50), wedge angle = 90 deg
# Validates: Fermat path, Keller cone, UTD D1-D4 vs K&P (1974)
o face0
v 2.0 0.0 -50.0
v 2.0 -50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 -50.0 50.0
v 2.0 0.0 50.0
vn 0.0 1.0 0.0
f 1//1 2//1 3//1
f 1//1 3//1 4//1

o faceN
v 2.0 0.0 -50.0
v 50.0 0.0 -50.0
v 50.0 0.0 50.0
v 2.0 0.0 50.0
vn 0.0 -1.0 0.0
f 5//2 7//2 6//2
f 6//2 7//2 8//2
